    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Live Streaming and Gameplay Welcome!!</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>**[Calligraphy Simulator Game]**</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Write characters on Japanese calligraphy paper using a brush. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy the art of calligraphy on your computer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully reproduce the brush techniques like *tome*, *hane*, and *harai*!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304490/extras/ce8abcc03c2815a31b543b3d47125eb7.poster.avif?t=1731578220\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304490/extras/ce8abcc03c2815a31b543b3d47125eb7.webm?t=1731578220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304490/extras/ce8abcc03c2815a31b543b3d47125eb7.mp4?t=1731578220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**[Hiragana &amp; Katakana]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn how to write hiragana and katakana by tracing the 50-syllable charts.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**[Calligraphy Practice]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practice calligraphy following examples and get used to brush movements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are various examples, including single characters, two characters, four-character idioms, and large-format paper.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**[Sutra Copying]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handwrite the *Heart Sutra* and engrave its sacred words into your heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It could also be used as a form of atonement, like waterfall meditation.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**[Kanji Test]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test yourself on the kanji learned in elementary school.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Self-score and check whether you got them right!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >**[Free Mode]**</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In different settings, feel free to write anything with a brush.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
